---
title: One-Pot Creamy Chicken, Bacon & Corn Soup with Wholemeal Panini
description: Is this chicken soup, the answer is almost but this bowl of warm flavours has some hidden gems waiting in the broth. The golden pops of sweetcorn are easy to spot and the roast veggies with bacon are a delight to taste. This is truly a bowl of bliss.
